text:
Stayed for couple nights during trip to Jakarta. It us actually more like service apartments style. 

Pluses:

- very good central location;
- big well equipped rooms;
- have small kitchen and washing machine;
- nice view ;
- very friendly, super helpful staff. Very good service!
- nice small gym and saunas;
- nice swimming pool;
- very good breakfast. 

Minuses:
- had slight smoking smell. Have to ask for non-smoking room before!
- water in pool was a bit cold;
- my friends were given fruit plate every day. Me - non. Haha . Minor small problems though. 

In general would recommend.
